{"id":133760,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/01/简讯：家乐福沃尔玛被指价格欺诈/","date":"2011-01-27T04:50:27Z","modified":"2011-01-27T04:50:27Z","title":"简讯：家乐福沃尔玛被指价格欺诈","content":"<div>\n<p>大型国际化连锁超市集团家乐福和沃尔玛在中国的数家超市因涉价格欺诈被处罚。</p>\n<p>国家发改委价检司称，这些超市存在虚构原价、低价招徕顾客高价结算、不履行价格承诺、误导性价格标示等多种价格欺诈行为。</p>\n<p>有关事件由媒体报道曝光后，有关超市已经受到处罚。</p>\n<p>国家发改委还要求中国所有超市和百货立即进行自查。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/SWLSY2lZGB21oQVt2Gz7lzLDm1Y/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/SWLSY2lZGB21oQVt2Gz7lzLDm1Y/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/SWLSY2lZGB21oQVt2Gz7lzLDm1Y/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/SWLSY2lZGB21oQVt2Gz7lzLDm1Y/1/di\"></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=TfMJRAs-CTU:To0n8daZl7Y:mqyYa2mfVbY\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=mqyYa2mfVbY\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=TfMJRAs-CTU:To0n8daZl7Y:PFx2F_oWK34\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=PFx2F_oWK34\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=TfMJRAs-CTU:To0n8daZl7Y:DUWcskeyX7o\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=DUWcskeyX7o\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=TfMJRAs-CTU:To0n8daZl7Y:clraHZBW0_I\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=clraHZBW0_I\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=TfMJRAs-CTU:To0n8daZl7Y:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=TfMJRAs-CTU:To0n8daZl7Y:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/TfMJRAs-CTU\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<h4>要翻墙? <a href=\"http://9293.biz\">用赛风</a>.</h4>\n","auth